devdoc.details: This contract allows users to create, manage, and interact with their personal shopping lists.

addItem(string,string,uint256).details: Adds an item with a specified name and quantity to a specific list created by the sender.

params.itemName: The name of the item to add.
params.listName: The name of the list to add the item to.
params.quantity: The quantity of the item to add.

createList(string).details: Creates a new shopping list for the sender with the specified name.

params.name: The name of the list to create.

getItemNames(string).details: Retrieves the names of all items in a specific list created by the sender.

params.listName: The name of the list to retrieve item names from.

returns._0: An array of strings containing the names of the items in the list.

getListNames().details: Retrieves the names of all lists created by the sender.

returns._0: An array of strings containing the names of the lists.
